Module downfall
Package downfall.realm

Class Actor

  • java.lang.Object
    • downfall.realm.Actor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Realm
    public abstract class Actor
extends java.lang.Object
    Actor is a basis common for all entities that can build or store or act on the board in any way shape or form.

      • Actor

        public Actor​(java.lang.Integer id,
             java.lang.String name,
             java.lang.Integer treasury)
        Using this constructor stockpile, ownedBuildings, and tags remain empty lists.
        Parameters:
        id - Unique actor identifier. Should be unique for every save file
        name - A human-readable name of the actor as a property.
        treasury - Amount of money in the treasury as a property.

      • Actor

             javafx.collections.ObservableList<Building> ownedBuildings,
             javafx.collections.ObservableList<Tag> tags)
        Parameters:
        id - Unique actor identifier. Should be unique for every save file
        name - A human-readable name of the actor as a property.
        treasury - Amount of money in the treasury as a property.
        stockpile - List of all materials in actor's stockpile
        ownedBuildings - List of all owned buildings
        tags - List of all tags applied to the actor
